{"tid":2198039,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撤逾千解放軍背景留學生簽證  美封殺中共「國防七校」","createTime":"2020-09-11T05:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T07:28:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bcda955aa9a1ba3a62125443da2121387995c6ca","tid":2198039,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:19:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200911/4NKU43UP2VFRZDXOKXETY5H47U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200911%2F4NKU43UP2VFRZDXOKXETY5H47U%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fjJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=50029c48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200911%2F4NKU43UP2VFRZDXOKXETY5H47U%2F&h=fd815c35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200911/4NKU43UP2VFRZDXOKXETY5H47U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n撤逾千解放軍背景留學生簽證 <br />\n美封殺中共「國防七校」<br />\n<br />\n【中美交鋒】美國國務院發言人稱截至周三，美國已撤銷超過1,000名中國留學生及研究人員的簽證，相信他們與軍方背景有關。根據撤銷簽證的留學生及研究生自行統計，受影響都是有中國「國防七校」背景的。有美國律師稱這批身在美國的學生不會被驅逐出境，但相信身在中國的美國留學生將難以入境。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：華限科技出口 TikTok難趕及轉讓<br />\n<br />\n今次禁令來自美國總統特朗普今年5月29日下達，限制中國學生或研究人員利用「F1」（學生簽證）及「J1」（訪問學者）簽證進。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZSCEbELhgPrUFSVfF0h9A-yft9I=/3780x2417/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SF7OBDVXXVA6XAIZDZQV5JKI7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZSCEbELhgPrUFSVfF0h9A-yft9I%3D%2F3780x2417%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSF7OBDVXXVA6XAIZDZQV5JKI7A.jpg&h=731bb1a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國撤銷逾1,000名中國留學生簽證，指他們有軍方背景；圖為前年中美關係未轉壞前，兩軍於南京交流。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北京「軍民混合取技術」<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人昨稱，美國截至當地時間周三已撤銷超過1,000名中國留學生及研究人員的簽證，相信他們與軍方背景有關，危害國家安全。發言人形容這些「高危學生及學者只佔中國留學生的一小部份」，強調仍然歡迎合法的學生及學者到美國。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大陸軍演逼近挑釁 台︰絕不退縮<br />\n<br />\n被撤銷簽證的留學生在群組統計，只有持F1、H1B（技術類工作人士簽證）和B簽證（商務及旅途簽證）人士遭撤銷。。。。。。。。。。。。北京郵電大學並不是國防七校之一，但在防衞及科技安全研究在中國具有盛名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qFjEzBlwk9Ko8_BvfvtFHs4WZUI=/615x758/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KELUHF4N2NFA5HUCW3GDWN7F3Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqFjEzBlwk9Ko8_BvfvtFHs4WZUI%3D%2F615x758%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKELUHF4N2NFA5HUCW3GDWN7F3Y.gif&h=3dec8f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受影響華學生擬興訟<br />\n<br />\n曾在美國國務院簽證處任職、現專門負責移民的律師Jeffrey Gorsky稱，美國國務院確有權取消任何簽證，理論上簽證取消後可被隨即遞解出境，但現實很少出現，原因是有可能違憲。因此，如果身在美國境內被取消簽證，只要有合理逗留原因如讀書，仍然是合法身份，只是取消了「入境許可」，即出境後無法再入境美國。不過，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"0c8cdb747a87f5051e7f4752f169b8055f27b1b6","tid":2198039,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"又分化中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62002c1e07cd55e11deb45f669431314eee87c2","tid":2198039,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"咁樣俾人屈法<br />\n俾我就自殺明志"},{"pid":"dccc6b9a9471f0ba2811dd913218007adc9ca45a","tid":2198039,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:49:50.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a304c0b33ecb0656fd6c215d52def61aa2bf70b","tid":2198039,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:56:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ea95d3d5df2b966d01d3ff4032b5a679c39f6be","tid":2198039,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T06:57:29.000Z","msg":"法拉里大平賣<img src=\"/assets/face